<font color="yellow">Kami dari kepolisian.</font>

531
00:53:23,035 --> 00:53:25,991
<font color="yellow"><i>Biksu Myung Chul. Park Bong Pal.</i></font>

532
00:53:36,613 --> 00:53:38,481
<font color="yellow">Silahkan masuk.</font>

533
00:53:47,613 --> 00:53:49,903
<font color="yellow">Maaf aku bertamu kemari...</font>

534
00:53:49,903 --> 00:53:51,899
<font color="yellow">...di saat kau sedang berduka.</font>

535
00:53:51,899 --> 00:53:53,970
<font color="yellow">Tidak apa-apa.</font>

536
00:53:55,702 --> 00:53:58,169
<font color="yellow">Apa hasil otopsinya sudah keluar?</font>

537
00:53:58,435 --> 00:54:00,546
<font color="yellow">Ya.</font>

538
00:54:01,524 --> 00:54:06,281
<font color="yellow">Sepertinya ayahmu dibunuh.</font>

539
00:54:08,991 --> 00:54:11,899
<font color="yellow">Jadi kami ingin bertanya padamu.</font>

540
00:54:11,899 --> 00:54:17,147
<font color="yellow">Apa kau tahu bagaimana
ayahmu kenal Profesor Joo?</font>

541
00:54:19,435 --> 00:54:21,524
<font color="yellow">Profesor Joo?</font>

542
00:54:23,747 --> 00:54:28,138
<font color="yellow">Apa dia ada kaitannya
dengan kematian ayahku?</font>

543
00:54:28,138 --> 00:54:31,481
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak yakin,
tapi ada kemungkinannya.</font>

544
00:54:32,569 --> 00:54:35,118
<font color="yellow">Jadi, katakan padaku
apa yang kauketahui.</font>

545
00:54:35,118 --> 00:54:37,347
<font color="yellow">Meskipun cuma sedikit
yang kau tahu.</font>

546
00:54:57,035 --> 00:55:00,059
<font color="yellow">Biksu Myung Chul, di mana kau?</font>

547
00:55:00,970 --> 00:55:02,836
<font color="yellow">Biksu Myung Chul.</font>

548
00:55:04,635 --> 00:55:08,613
<font color="yellow">Apa kebetulan kau tahu tentang hal itu?</font>

549
00:55:08,680 --> 00:55:10,769
<font color="yellow">Apa maksudmu?</font>

550
00:55:13,281 --> 00:55:15,859
<font color="yellow">Detektif tadi datang.</font>

551
00:55:17,258 --> 00:55:20,169
<font color="yellow">Dia bertanya tentang Profesor Joo.</font>

552
00:55:22,702 --> 00:55:31,546
<font color="yellow">Profesor Joo ada kaitannya
dengan kematian ayahku.</font>

553
00:55:32,991 --> 00:55:35,035
<font color="yellow">Bong Pal.</font>

554
00:55:39,769 --> 00:55:42,013
<font color="yellow">Profesor Joo itu bukan manusia.</font>

555
00:55:42,859 --> 00:55:45,147
<font color="yellow">Aku yakin sekali...</font>

556
00:55:45,191 --> 00:55:50,059
<font color="yellow">...ada roh jahat yang ada
di dalam tubuhnya.</font>

557
00:55:51,059 --> 00:55:52,903
<font color="yellow">Roh jahat.</font>

558
00:55:55,635 --> 00:56:00,080
<font color="yellow">Roh jahat yang dulu sekali keluar dari
tubuhmu...</font>

559
00:56:00,080 --> 00:56:05,214
<font color="yellow">...yang selalu berada
mengawasimu dan Hyun Ji.</font>

560
00:56:06,680 --> 00:56:07,897
<font color="yellow">Hyun Ji?</font>

561
00:56:07,897 --> 00:56:10,412
<font color="yellow"><i>Hyun Ji memliki benda yang
sangat diinginkan oleh roh itu. </i></font>

562
00:56:24,303 --> 00:56:26,370
<font color="yellow">Kenapa?</font>

563
00:56:26,502 --> 00:56:29,613
<font color="yellow">Aku merasa pusing.</font>

564
00:56:30,502 --> 00:56:33,591
<font color="yellow">Aku mau ke kamar kecil dulu.</font>

565
00:56:55,147 --> 00:56:57,792
<font color="yellow"><i>[Kekasihku Bong Bong]</i></font>

566
00:57:06,414 --> 00:57:09,680
<font color="yellow"><i>Panggilan Anda sedang dialihkan...</i></font>

567
00:58:06,646 --> 00:58:19,901
